  "text": [
    "As soon as",
    "I speak, I",
    "speaks. It",
    "wants to",
    "be free but",
    "impassive lies",
    "in the direction",
    "of its",
    "words. Let",
    "x equal x, x",
    "also",
    "equals x. I",
    "speak to",
    "hear myself",
    "speak? I",
    "had not thought",
    "that some-",
    "thing had such",
    "undone. It",
    "was an idea",
    "of mine."
  ],
  "title": "The Pattern",
  "year": ""
